# Cooperative Evaluation Rules - Peer Review, Praise, Approach Classification

@prefix qp: <https://qualia.org/ontology/cooperative-projects#> .
@prefix wf: <https://wellfair.org/ns#> .
@prefix math: <http://www.w3.org/2000/10/swap/math#> .

# Classify Approach Type
{ ?proj qp:approachType ?type . } => { ?proj wf:classifiedApproach true . } .

# Technical Debt Impact on Multiplier
{ ?proj qp:technicalDebtLevel ?debt . ?proj qp:expectedMultiplier ?base . } => { (?base (?debt 0.3 math:product) math:subtract) ?adjusted . ?proj qp:expectedMultiplier ?adjusted . } .

# Reward Multiplier Calculation
{ ?idea qp:approachType qp:RiskyApproach . } => { ?idea qp:expectedMultiplier 12.0 . } .

{ ?idea qp:approachType qp:OptimalApproach . } => { ?idea qp:expectedMultiplier 1.8 . } .